{"tid":47303,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"【我找到北了】漠河北極村","createTime":"2016-12-20T09:02:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-13T01:40:46.000Z","uid":37661,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b5cd6f2f6fb30c4320ff3615b753301f71c7438d","tid":47303,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:02:40.000Z","msg":"火車去到漠河，再包車入北極村，去到天都黑晒。(依家火車去無以前咁耐時間)<br />\n<br />\n到埗零下30度<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/D_zpsxohv0dcm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FD_zpsxohv0dcm.jpg&h=c43508b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二天包佐架馬拉雪撬作北極村遊覽<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0197_zpsufpmc8vj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0197_zpsufpmc8vj.jpg&h=64b64e2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沿黑龍江上邊行，一片冰天雪地<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0201_zpsrdvg93ey.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0201_zpsrdvg93ey.jpg&h=56f03e71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n坐在雪撬上，雖然蓋著厚氈，但係一樣咁凍，尤其係腳指，耐唔耐都要落地行，等血氣運行，否則腳指會凍壞。<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0206_zps4nozhbw6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0206_zps4nozhbw6.jpg&h=b1caf8f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你唔會分到你係在陸地上定係黑龍江面上<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0213_zpst0fwyd0e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0213_zpst0fwyd0e.jpg&h=39f7b4b2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1297ab17995d284aeceab3fc9eb2829e92be8d99","tid":47303,"uid":995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:03:20.000Z","msg":"正呀"},{"pid":"5f7bcc5751f8bf40c0324f6bf360efcd9570d079","tid":47303,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:03:34.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"468330d071a4a6e98448d00e999d57a6ba369a95","tid":47303,"uid":995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:03:50.000Z","msg":"巴打咁凍要着咩衫去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1c75f2662c3312e207305f0d562149965feb0ab","tid":47303,"uid":33749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:06:15.000Z","msg":"留名跟進"},{"pid":"6c0b0ec59ce8bcf0b0830339160bf520abb9e3af","tid":47303,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:07:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打咁凍要着咩衫去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最外層 Goretex 風褸鎖住內層既抓毛褸同埋其他保暖衣 (外層加埋4件+快乾衣底底)<br />\n<br />\n下身一條厚抓毛褲再加條可防水的不太厚雪褲。"},{"pid":"00acbdda553b7358cd3f4c1b195662e0ed5243f9","tid":47303,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:14:08.000Z","msg":"帶着我地果個拉馬人係山東人，連佢自己都話凍，不過為搵食無法子。<br />\n<br />\n先帶我地去滑雪坡 (無相片)，滑完帶我地去一戶人家裡食飯。<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0219_zpsntgfyecb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0219_zpsntgfyecb.jpg&h=f169e9bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入到去，個個都腳指凍到好痛，相機入到室內，無保護下，鏡頭鏡片都結冰，結果<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0257_zpsbqeibd2z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0257_zpsbqeibd2z.jpg&h=81941cc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n要用體溫溶晒啲霜先可以繼續影相<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0263_zpsq7vf9o21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0263_zpsq7vf9o21.jpg&h=f4d2164a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑龍江對面的俄羅斯<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0268_zpsb5nsse0w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0268_zpsb5nsse0w.jpg&h=eaaf61bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國界界碑，圍繞着國界都會有好多個。<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0286_zpssic03voe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0286_zpssic03voe.jpg&h=598aa6f7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"474b3611bdf14af87b9f8b19a4e485a47de57bd5","tid":47303,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T04:25:29.000Z","msg":"北極埡口廣場<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0287_zpsm3yase6v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0287_zpsm3yase6v.jpg&h=7f523ff3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0288_zpsmg1fmffu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0288_zpsmg1fmffu.jpg&h=4516b246&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n北極村雪雕<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0303_zps2igmaqx4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0303_zps2igmaqx4.jpg&h=c29429c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0308_zpsiqwco45l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0308_zpsiqwco45l.jpg&h=2bad4c28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國北極點<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0310_zpstixactcc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0310_zpstixactcc.jpg&h=43a82280&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最北屎坑<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0314_zpskkxw0loo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0314_zpskkxw0loo.jpg&h=7b5a85d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廣場全景<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0317_zpsxlnjws8h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0317_zpsxlnjws8h.jpg&h=5754f15e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我找到北了<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0318_zpshub3jc0i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0318_zpshub3jc0i.jpg&h=a99baed8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"047c244ec9a0ea0ec8191db32bef76bf5b1946f6","tid":47303,"uid":19310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T05:18:12.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"63de3ee8c5e1c4a53627d6e39df25257ed555357","tid":47303,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T09:18:48.000Z","msg":"北緯 53.3度<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0321_zps7m0yk65q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0321_zps7m0yk65q.jpg&h=6d3be48c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0326_zpsdvib8ozi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0326_zpsdvib8ozi.jpg&h=c3ac4f51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n冰封了的黑龍江遊船<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0330_zpsgyes6azv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0330_zpsgyes6azv.jpg&h=7b9fafcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n北極村<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0334_zpsqvsahpok.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0334_zpsqvsahpok.jpg&h=12f28e89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0335_zpscfsvyvwk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0335_zpscfsvyvwk.jpg&h=f03d282b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0345_zpspdkvxpxu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0345_zpspdkvxpxu.jpg&h=b9b7a910&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0346_zpsixr29uj1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0346_zpsixr29uj1.jpg&h=b6b04a8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0353_zps4dmv33fx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0353_zps4dmv33fx.jpg&h=3dcfd8a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ef2b5e47b568f7adf73a35785a3761121b471d2f","tid":47303,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T09:22:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0367_zpsoljbbwbp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0367_zpsoljbbwbp.jpg&h=b90dd2be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0368_zpspdxmz2a9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0368_zpspdxmz2a9.jpg&h=231760f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0370_zpsqzcks5yf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0370_zpsqzcks5yf.jpg&h=8bb81fbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑龍江冰面上的中俄邊界，但係過界無人理。<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0377_zpshqxnlejp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0377_zpshqxnlejp.jpg&h=773a94d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n北極村日落<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0385_zpsl33fooxa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0385_zpsl33fooxa.jpg&h=3be5ce37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當地兒童及冰滑梯，滑梯滑落黑龍江江面<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0390_zpseb2nwyzl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0390_zpseb2nwyzl.jpg&h=132fe63f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0392_zpsffr9tutn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0392_zpsffr9tutn.jpg&h=2d670d99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0398_zpse2kfet31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0398_zpse2kfet31.jpg&h=9e9a1586&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"575f03dc574c978075476fb0e76f7b8b443f505f","tid":47303,"uid":41562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T09:55:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4fdc461b40ee0eb437ece4172b97f3b77747674","tid":47303,"uid":4072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T07:30:18.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"2079cee5531209ff8185ee8a13eb075302e8aacb","tid":47303,"uid":38679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T12:23:58.000Z","msg":"今日到漠河，落雪，得-20度"},{"pid":"c56fd436179d21bec4591aaf9fceb53b28c10782","tid":47303,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T12:32:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今日到漠河，落雪，得-20度</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁暖。<br />\n<br />\n哈爾濱人都話負廿度都叫做唔凍。"},{"pid":"e2e6b03450e7fade446f304273790f11164a7093","tid":47303,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T12:52:14.000Z","msg":"北極村日出，專登一早去爬山睇日出，凍唔凍？唔記得了。<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0426_zpscgbgravw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0426_zpscgbgravw.jpg&h=1c88ca77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0438_zpssd9ijmt3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0438_zpssd9ijmt3.jpg&h=28f3c247&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0443_zpsoac1ujeo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0443_zpsoac1ujeo.jpg&h=991061cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0444_zpslwegumdk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0444_zpslwegumdk.jpg&h=f517fb0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0445_zps9wpujwor.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0445_zps9wpujwor.jpg&h=884669ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n爬上去就辛苦，落就好正，因為可以在雪上面滑落嚟。<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0459_zpsju7pn9yg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0459_zpsju7pn9yg.jpg&h=39563dfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n負38度啦喂。<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0462_zps1ncd1qwp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0462_zps1ncd1qwp.jpg&h=1767675f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c6a0bbe189794e4e35a56fa4cb71db58a15001fc","tid":47303,"uid":52623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T12:53:26.000Z","msg":"我當年去哈爾濱都係零下廿度。學識著衫之後就唔覺得凍。<br />\n<br />\n之前十十下，亂咁著，凍到抽根"},{"pid":"a380807ec3b59da370b68e7341227b034a0e8d39","tid":47303,"uid":52623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T12:55:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>火車去到漠河，再包車入北極村，去到天都黑晒。(依家火車去無以前咁耐時間)<br />\n<br />\n到埗零下30度<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/D_zpsxohv0dcm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FD_zpsxohv0dcm.jpg&h=c43508b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二天包佐架馬拉雪撬作北極村遊覽<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0197_zpsufpmc8vj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0197_zpsufpmc8vj.jpg&h=64b64e2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沿黑龍江上邊行，一片冰天雪地<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0201_zpsrdvg93ey.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0201_zpsrdvg93ey.jpg&h=56f03e71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n坐在雪撬上，雖然蓋著厚氈，但係一樣咁凍，尤其係腳指，耐唔耐都要落地行，等血氣運行，否則腳指會凍壞。<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0206_zps4nozhbw6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0206_zps4nozhbw6.jpg&h=b1caf8f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你唔會分到你係在陸地上定係黑龍江面上<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0213_zpst0fwyd0e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0213_zpst0fwyd0e.jpg&h=39f7b4b2&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你咩月份去？"},{"pid":"6b7525dd447a5788ca491f26b95b5e73dcd13601","tid":47303,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T12:57:00.000Z","msg":"最後北極村的早上<br />\n<br />\n北極哨所<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0466_zpsjeyt7v5f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0466_zpsjeyt7v5f.jpg&h=84461a30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑龍江對面俄羅斯村莊 (或軍營) ZOOM 近咗<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0468_zpsqusqxyir.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0468_zpsqusqxyir.jpg&h=1b4a7eab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無 ZOOM<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0477_zps5r9dhybu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0477_zps5r9dhybu.jpg&h=e84a07a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當地官員官邸<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0479_zpsol6a6rkm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0479_zpsol6a6rkm.jpg&h=db0b8f3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最北郵局<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0482_zps9z0hkluh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0482_zps9z0hkluh.jpg&h=0c9c8fc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當時可以自己俾數碼相佢做POST CARD，即做即有，果陣都算幾新既野。<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0483_zpsqsrlxx6n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0483_zpsqsrlxx6n.jpg&h=242956bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當進入北極村就會見到呢塊大石。<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0485_zpsmytghdon.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0485_zpsmytghdon.jpg&h=ef480e09&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8b91ed97562e2e44681ed1749429bcc62114412d","tid":47303,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T12:58:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你咩月份去？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n二月份，啱啱農曆新年無耐，仲要啲保暖嘢全部都買唔到。"},{"pid":"79f057df3a0bafbec572a4c2cd1c59e6989d2aa9","tid":47303,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T13:36:18.000Z","msg":"室內暖氣通常開幾度"},{"pid":"d691692ac5127d6d0b21edbc2bf1cf513db2a786","tid":47303,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T13:37:30.000Z","msg":"支那扮北極？"},{"pid":"30a136eded3297ee498670399851f33e7e56a3ff","tid":47303,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T13:40:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>室內暖氣通常開幾度</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n廿幾度。<br />\n<br />\n一入去就要搏命除。"},{"pid":"d7c39405b68347a12fb8c8415b9de792a0cdf3d1","tid":47303,"uid":60639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T14:09:14.000Z","msg":"好正 留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9caf8093d1ebf7ae2d6e9bd6c71e89bbf3f13922","tid":47303,"uid":41562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T15:26:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"283b43fc1c43a4441bccc4b28618eefd5a330d59","tid":47303,"uid":52623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T16:53:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你咩月份去？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n二月份，啱啱農曆新年無耐，仲要啲保暖嘢全部都買唔到。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05ec3e9ddd878dde867a402870fe56cd59279de1","tid":47303,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T17:49:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5257f23cc88bb97748aa467dcef30f61e4e0096","tid":47303,"uid":995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T18:18:26.000Z","msg":"真係好正<br />\n原本諗住今個sem break 去 不過唔得了"},{"pid":"c346185ae43f3562a76578a83131ec898c487b63","tid":47303,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T01:45:25.000Z","msg":"當日我地坐雪撬出去，有啲人腳指都凍到腫晒，要用雪同佢擦腳消腫，仲要佢地都着梗哈爾濱買既雪鞋。<br />\n<br />\n去到果間農家院，要除晒鞋襪圍著火爐取暖，腳指先有番知覺。<br />\n<br />\n零下30度以下有幾凍？<br />\n<br />\n鼻孔呼氣會在鼻哥窿下面結霜。<br />\n<br />\n如果你戴佐MASK，啲水氣向上升，就到你眼睫毛結霜。<br />\n<br />\n有戴眼鏡仲大鑊，水氣去佐眼鏡片，到眼鏡片結冰，點抹都抹唔甩。<br />\n<br />\n影相，有時塊面掂到金屬機身都會黏實佐。<br />\n<br />\n在北極村逗留佐兩晚，第三日就由包車師傅送我地去洛古村再返漠河縣。<br />\n<br />\n這邊都是這種樹，長得高但是很幼。(俄羅斯西伯利亞鐵路見都係咁上下既樹)<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0486_zpspdnlk0n7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0486_zpspdnlk0n7.jpg&h=a2003ad8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢段路仲有剷雪車將雪剷向兩邊。<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0488_zpsttecwudy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0488_zpsttecwudy.jpg&h=b72dc8cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢段通往洛古村的山路，唔知以為係上面俾雪撬滑落嚟既賽道。<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0492_zpsq6cp9o1n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0492_zpsq6cp9o1n.jpg&h=cdd899ae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"977f62cafc2e74ba37e97e38bc1b6c54491cccc5","tid":47303,"uid":68392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T01:58:44.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"500f876b1eca73e658845dbf2bd00da6ec8014f3","tid":47303,"uid":26115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T02:03:16.000Z","msg":"前年由香港(20度左右)飛去北京(8度左右)，再搭一晚火車去哈爾濱(-26度)，一日經歷40度溫差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n落火車果下清晨黎涷撚到痴線...."},{"pid":"5e7d96f634163051de34598e0dc3ed293b53ba90","tid":47303,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T02:08:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前年由香港(20度左右)飛去北京(8度左右)，再搭一晚火車去哈爾濱(-26度)，一日經歷40度溫差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n落火車果下清晨黎涷撚到痴線....</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係飛機去，夜晚到哈爾濱機場，未落機就報氣溫係零下20度，成班機啲人嘩嘩聲。<br />\n<br />\n仲要衰到班機無得泊橋，要落機轉巴士，個身應該著既衫頂多可以頂到十度八度。<br />\n<br />\n啲厚衫全部寄晒倉，等落機先有得著番。<br />\n<br />\n後尾好多嘢都在哈爾濱買，又平又暖。"},{"pid":"4e86d61410a2be93c2d2221a822aa8272abc567a","tid":47303,"uid":26115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T02:21:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>前年由香港(20度左右)飛去北京(8度左右)，再搭一晚火車去哈爾濱(-26度)，一日經歷40度溫差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n落火車果下清晨黎涷撚到痴線....</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係飛機去，夜晚到哈爾濱機場，未落機就報氣溫係零下20度，成班機啲人嘩嘩聲。<br />\n<br />\n仲要衰到班機無得泊橋，要落機轉巴士，個身應該著既衫頂多可以頂到十度八度。<br />\n<br />\n啲厚衫全部寄晒倉，等落機先有得著番。<br />\n<br />\n後尾好多嘢都在哈爾濱買，又平又暖。</blockquote><br />\n去之前淘寶左D羊毛厚襪同底衫，全部性價化都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當地買左雪帽同雪鞋，但覺得D雪鞋太柒都係着番對timberland，加埋對厚襪都夠做，行山果陣鞋頭結哂冰，頭髮又結哂冰，好誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8920e19c885403c2dabb3d3d1c7f26b4344698b1","tid":47303,"uid":24883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T10:04:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 負廿度<br />\n想問下 啲衫去到當地買會平啲定係買定過去平"},{"pid":"45b5d019c84194d1e7440e68905d55993b17a8a3","tid":47303,"uid":6495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T10:50:35.000Z","msg":"Total用左幾錢？"},{"pid":"76a1bd3ace2d7e0bd36d01e7c12c046276c5e321","tid":47303,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T12:03:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 負廿度<br />\n想問下 啲衫去到當地買會平啲定係買定過去平</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依家就淘寶啦。<br />\n<br />\n去到唔夠先加咋。"},{"pid":"0a88fbfc2cf6f7d7741a16e0ddc4c849095ea2c3","tid":47303,"uid":24883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T12:06:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 負廿度<br />\n想問下 啲衫去到當地買會平啲定係買定過去平</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依家就淘寶啦。<br />\n<br />\n去到唔夠先加咋。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nThx bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b11b4a973a5a4382ad1408134d3e94558a85afde","tid":47303,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T14:19:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Total用左幾錢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你計掂香港去哈爾濱交通先，其他喺漠河北極村消費貴極有限。<br />\n<br />\n但你要計埋哈爾濱會玩啲乜，睇啲乜？<br />\n<br />\n入場費加加埋埋唔少。<br />\n<br />\n你去滑雪又可以係一條大數。"},{"pid":"91d8621ef57043e1b6dae522842e46df8b204e97","tid":47303,"uid":6495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T14:39:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Total用左幾錢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你計掂香港去哈爾濱交通先，其他喺漠河北極村消費貴極有限。<br />\n<br />\n但你要計埋哈爾濱會玩啲乜，睇啲乜？<br />\n<br />\n入場費加加埋埋唔少。<br />\n<br />\n你去滑雪又可以係一條大數。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係呀我係想問你呢個旅程用左幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16433fd2f359c0a6af73c5232f4939ca0a55738a","tid":47303,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T14:41:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Total用左幾錢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你計掂香港去哈爾濱交通先，其他喺漠河北極村消費貴極有限。<br />\n<br />\n但你要計埋哈爾濱會玩啲乜，睇啲乜？<br />\n<br />\n入場費加加埋埋唔少。<br />\n<br />\n你去滑雪又可以係一條大數。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係呀我係想問你呢個旅程用左幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n機票去左成五千，因為早一個星期買就出發。<br />\n<br />\n其他冇計到"},{"pid":"51fbc8380ed3f9a7d7a6c85bc7b9fd3d6901c2ce","tid":47303,"uid":38679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T15:27:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你計掂香港去哈爾濱交通先，其他喺漠河北極村消費貴極有限。<br />\n<br />\n但你要計埋哈爾濱會玩啲乜，睇啲乜？<br />\n<br />\n入場費加加埋埋唔少。<br />\n<br />\n你去滑雪又可以係一條大數。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係呀我係想問你呢個旅程用左幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n機票去左成五千，因為早一個星期買就出發。<br />\n<br />\n其他冇計到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n飛瀋陽，然後搭火車去哈爾濱，哈爾濱再搭火車去漠河，會平d"},{"pid":"2a14acbe25231ba4f32044403a486fab7994d6a2","tid":47303,"uid":52623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T15:27:41.000Z","msg":"滑雪唔係好貴。<br />\n<br />\n晌東三省省會城市可以參加即日來回既團。我幾年前俾左每人約二百"},{"pid":"3937f2835b266b5f19726912d9e216ad46db5c2a","tid":47303,"uid":67878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T16:01:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"402055e4fe0b9015b2af15fc9d1be1309d9b0fa6","tid":47303,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T02:20:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>滑雪唔係好貴。<br />\n<br />\n晌東三省省會城市可以參加即日來回既團。我幾年前俾左每人約二百</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nlocal 團帶你去果啲場好流，似樣啲都要加錢或自己去。<br />\n<br />\n唔洗錢嘅話，去開冰雪大世界都有得滑啦。"},{"pid":"10a24bd027b6f5d1c3ba04c66606a6a70942b0ff","tid":47303,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T02:28:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你計掂香港去哈爾濱交通先，其他喺漠河北極村消費貴極有限。<br />\n<br />\n但你要計埋哈爾濱會玩啲乜，睇啲乜？<br />\n<br />\n入場費加加埋埋唔少。<br />\n<br />\n你去滑雪又可以係一條大數。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係呀我係想問你呢個旅程用左幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n機票去左成五千，因為早一個星期買就出發。<br />\n<br />\n其他冇計到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n飛瀋陽，然後搭火車去哈爾濱，哈爾濱再搭火車去漠河，會平d</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n直接廣州坐36個鐘去哈爾濱仲平。"},{"pid":"47c08edb30e1fafebea67e2236dcb7a771bdde9d","tid":47303,"uid":52623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T04:55:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>滑雪唔係好貴。<br />\n<br />\n晌東三省省會城市可以參加即日來回既團。我幾年前俾左每人約二百</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nlocal 團帶你去果啲場好流，似樣啲都要加錢或自己去。<br />\n<br />\n唔洗錢嘅話，去開冰雪大世界都有得滑啦。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啲團寫明去邊個場，淘寶上面大把。自己揀"},{"pid":"d7621d602b0aeaaf68b2b6f9ecb4dd7ceca090fc","tid":47303,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T00:37:09.000Z","msg":"由北極村過洛古村要80公里，其中30公里就兩邊有雪，另外果啲就全部雪路，上個帖有相，有雪路上真係可以架車踩到80公里，但見到有車一定要收慢。<br />\n<br />\n本來包車師傅想同我地開車落冰面上行，但後來話政府呢幾日禁咗唔俾落，結果只能人走黑龍江。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0494_zps25qyigiw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0494_zps25qyigiw.jpg&h=66f94d1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0495_zps3fuxnupp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0495_zps3fuxnupp.jpg&h=bad5dc6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0496_zpsa2srka3s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0496_zpsa2srka3s.jpg&h=719402cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日終於睇到人冰上補魚，冰上鑽洞然後放網捉魚，樹枝下面綁着個魚網，等一排先會拉番上嚟，但通常個窿都會結佐少少冰，要先再打通佢先。<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0497_zpsccb6cfgr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0497_zpsccb6cfgr.jpg&h=e78ebbf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n啲魚上水果陣仲識跳，但係唔夠半分鐘就會冰到硬咗。<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0508_zpsxj94pdla.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0508_zpsxj94pdla.jpg&h=43292faf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後我地幫當地人買咗啲魚返去加工，除咗呢網之外，另外再有另一網一齊拎去俾人煮。<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0509_zpsffuyc8nz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0509_zpsffuyc8nz.jpg&h=b74a5d47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實雪好厚，你唔會覺得自己係喺冰面上面。<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0510_zps4meks35h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0510_zps4meks35h.jpg&h=75a05e1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到有樹枝即係下面有魚網，背景為俄羅斯。<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0511_zpsy7rni3jw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0511_zpsy7rni3jw.jpg&h=c6f09bd7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3de9604d93f7d4dbed0adff599fd41db4b5bf565","tid":47303,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-12T13:51:59.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"cffd215dada56921a9b37cc68cb0c09b54662539","tid":47303,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-13T01:32:23.000Z","msg":"行完黑龍江，返到村內搵地方食晏晝飯，但發覺很多鋪頭都冇開，原來呢度既村民下晝好鍾意去打麻雀，後來搵到一間有開，問好價錢便留底喺度食。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0516_zpsaanixim4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0516_zpsaanixim4.jpg&h=2b8ebd44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食完飯就喺條村外面行，呢度啲村民養好多狗，都唔明點解啲狗唔怕凍，喺戶外咁耐都唔會變冰狗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0517_zps6veguwfb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0517_zps6veguwfb.jpg&h=b5190ffb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0522_zpshjjj8gxq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0522_zpshjjj8gxq.jpg&h=dfbba2f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0527_zpsgkq3defy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0527_zpsgkq3defy.jpg&h=0e1c3469&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n古洛村家家戶戶門前一左一右都有一個冰燈罩，裡面會放一盞油燈，係呢度既特色。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0528_zpsayikraqc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0528_zpsayikraqc.jpg&h=69a49d97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0530_zpsq8dz5ytd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0530_zpsq8dz5ytd.jpg&h=a8b801b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0533_zpsemgnv4dm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0533_zpsemgnv4dm.jpg&h=4f120347&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0542_zpskou67nri.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0542_zpskou67nri.jpg&h=43c3b84d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑龍江，對面為俄羅斯軍營<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0545_zpshjvhtrce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0545_zpshjvhtrce.jpg&h=c1f5a2e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0537_zpscuhn14pe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0537_zpscuhn14pe.jpg&h=8c24cf27&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6f4f61072800f66c474aaa9e5134c624600742aa","tid":47303,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-13T01:39:01.000Z","msg":"飯後喺洛古村行多陣就回程，回程經過一個李金鏞祠堂，都唔知係乜水，求其影幾張相就算，連行上去都唔行。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0549_zps1zvu69k4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0549_zps1zvu69k4.jpg&h=d407b112&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0550_zpsjzbrcpaj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0550_zpsjzbrcpaj.jpg&h=5dee8e11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0551_zpsbhiogkzg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0551_zpsbhiogkzg.jpg&h=dfa51240&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Arctic%20Village/DSC_0556_zps9af1ffmw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FArctic%2520Village%2FDSC_0556_zps9af1ffmw.jpg&h=b28a1f9b&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}